sentences: Dobkin moved to Los Angeles in 1976.
Along with Judith Owen, Dobkin participated in Richard Thompson's 1000 Years of Popular Music tour.
A 2005 concert of this show was released on CD and DVD in 2006.
In 2009, Dobkin also participated in Thompson's Cabaret of Souls song cycle project commissioned by the International Society of Bassists.
